      <title>菲律宾 125 亿美元零售债务到期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/philippines-retail-debt-in-the-works-as-12-5-billion-falls-due</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾财政部长表示，菲律宾将在第一季度向个人和其他散户投资者出售债券，利用金融体系中充足的现金为到期债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-19/philippines-retail-debt-in-the-works-as-12-5-billion-falls-due</guid>
